      <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-7">
        <h2>summer-mvc</h2>
        <p>
          <b>well formed IT</b> itself is small web application system. <br>
          So, it needed to control HTTP request and HTTP Response. <br>
          <br>
          For doing this, <b>well formed IT</b> is implemented with <b>summer-mvc</b> framework <br>which is Nodejs web application framework for speedy development. <br>
          All controllers, services and data accessing logics are using <b>summer-mvc</b>. <br>
          <br>
          <b>well formed IT</b> is opened for everyone. <br>
          And <b>summer-mvc</b> is also opened. <br>
          You can download, access and redesign our source code under <b>MIT</b> license.
        </p>

        <button class="btn btn-important" onclick="javascript:gotoAbout();">View Well Formed IT Architecture</button>
        <button class="btn btn-important" onclick="javascript:gotoSummerMVC();">Go To summer-mvc</button>
